{"tid":2025150,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實真係唔明為乜要內戰，有氣都留嚟屌建制啦","createTime":"2020-05-20T05:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T05:18:21.000Z","uid":40550,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"de1c3ed68733566463b92eb7ae1faf0123dfc6f3","tid":2025150,"uid":40550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"同以前熱狗狙擊白鴿一樣<br />\n白鴿又柒又蠢又走入中聯辦出賣香港人<br />\n但都叫做泛民<br />\n有氣都留嚟屌建制啦<br />\n<br />\n我覺得而家情況都類似<br />\n香港最近經歷緊咁大件社運事件，<br />\n唔好突然之間有閑情逸致去追擊網絡垃圾啦<br />\n佢哋幾垃圾幾冇品幾仆街都好<br />\n都叫做黃嗰邊<br />\n喺社運上面都叫做發揮過丁屎咁多影響力<br />\n建制更仆街嘅比比皆是<br />\n起碼留啲火力喺呢啲仆街身上<br />\n之後先再清算網絡垃圾<br />\n<br />\n先安內後攘外呀"},{"pid":"35e879aa386cdea202d22ece570c4822d00030c2","tid":2025150,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5a61279698d3f4d1a504a6c1514d225d4d03bad0","tid":2025150,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"（撐港台請入）停止干預香港電台、反對停播《頭條新聞》的公開聯署信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2025143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2025143</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec34e1ea0afabf7b0256f9a71086aa735ba5f0e8","tid":2025150,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9C76ch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9C76ch.jpg&h=49c531e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efb28ece267ed42395b36bb13d73f47f588c27b1","tid":2025150,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"冇錯 屌柒建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c723e65ce6207b80ff8ecbc66391e98f93d04f","tid":2025150,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84e2328c92d89e9fd6a7f305ab99910be